text: ( Source : Virginia Tech - Virginia Polytechnic Institute and State University ) Sean Collins BLACKSBURG, Va., Oct. 8, 2015 - The Pamplin College of Business has appointed Sean Collins as Innovate director in the college's Apex Systems Center
